rows.label: qst202019_msg0003
rows.name:
5 clumps of Salty Soil, 8 portions
of Folta, and 5 Ruby Mangosteens.

rows.label: qst202019_msg0101
rows.name:
Wow, thank you! You've gathered 
all the ingredients for me, haven't you?

rows.label: qst202019_msg0102

It must have been difficult to 
gather all of this, wasn't it?

rows.label: qst202019_msg0104
rows.name:
As thanks, though it's not much, 
please let me treat you to a meal.

rows.label: qst202019_msg0108
rows.name:
My home is beyond Treita Windmill Plaza. 
Please do come!
